This is a placeholder for the Assets.xcassets bundle.

To set up your asset catalog:

1. Delete this file and create an actual Assets.xcassets directory in Xcode.
2. Add your app icon set named "AppIcon" with all required sizes.
3. Add an "AccentColor" color set that matches {{PRIMARY_COLOR}}.
4. Add any image assets your views reference by name.

Required asset sets for this archetype:
- AppIcon (all sizes for iOS)
- AccentColor (color set, value: {{PRIMARY_COLOR}})
